            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Start by checking if <code>like_author</code> is <code>True</code>, then use <code>or</code> to check <code>like_genre</code>, and finally <code>got_recommendation</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"like_author = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"like_genre = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"got_recommendation = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" like_author \" /><text value=\"or\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" like_genre \" /><text value=\"or\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" got_recommendation:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Buy book&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"68\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"80\" endIndex=\"82\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"93\" /><option startIndex=\"94\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option startIndex=\"97\" endIndex=\"115\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"and\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Buy book\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>like_author</code> followed by <code>or</code> and then <code>like_genre</code>, <code>or</code>, <code>got_recommendation</code>.</p></body></html>"
